title: This Generations Godfather Soulja Boy
itunes:title: This Generations Godfather Soulja Boy
description:
Today on the show we had critically acclaimed godfather of this generation, Soulja Boy better known as "Young Draco" pull up on "The Breakfast Club" and he came to announce his worth. He spoke about influencing artist like Tekashi and even Drake!! and reclaims himself as the biggest comeback of 2018. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to yet another Floridian and and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
